Skills.Name: Spinning Slash
Skills.Description: Cancels all Debuff effects on all allies. Inflicts 3-hit DMG (<color=red>{1}%</color> + <color=red>{2}%</color> + <color=red>{3}%</color>) on single enemy. Also inflicts <code=400,param=206><color=#3398f1>Dark</color> for 5s. Further inflicts 3x <code=900,param=911><color=#3398f1>Twin Fang Seal</color> for 60s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Cancels Debuff effect(s) on all allies. Inflicts 3-hit DMG, Dark and Twin Fang Seal on single enemy

Skills.Name: Boomerang Storm
Skills.Description: Raises ATK of all Green Elemental allies by {0}% for 15s. Further raises Speed by {1}% for 15s. Inflicts <code=400,param=256><color=#3398f1>Weakness</color> ({2}% of skill user's ATK) on all enemies for 10s. Also inflicts 2-hit DMG (<color=red>{3}%</color> + <color=red>{4}%</color>). Further inflicts <code=400,param=203><color=#3398f1>Paralysis</color> for 3s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises ATK and Speed of all Green Elemental allies. Inflicts Weakness, 2-hit DMG and Paralysis on all enemies

Skills.Name: Destruction End
Skills.Description: Raises CRIT Rate of all Green Elemental allies by {0}% for 10s. Further raises CRIT ATK by {1}% for 10s. Lowers DEF of all enemies by {2}% for 10s. Further lowers ATK by {3}% for 10s. Raises own Hidden Technique DMG Limit by 30000 for 60s if the total number of <code=900,param=911><color=#3398f1>Twin Fang Seal</color> on all enemies is 50 or more. Inflicts 3-hit DMG (<color=red>{7}%</color> + <color=red>{8}%</color> + <color=red>{9}%</color>) on single enemy. Further inflicts {11}% DMG multiplied by total <color=#3398f1>Twin Fang Seal</color> (Stacked) on target (Max. {12}%).
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises CRIT Rate and CRIT ATK of all Green Elemental allies. Lowers DEF and ATK of all enemies. Raises own Hidden Technique DMG Limit if the total number of Twin Fang Seal on all enemies is 50 or more. Inflicts 3-hit DMG on single enemy. Further inflicts DMG based on that target's total Twin Fang Seal

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Inflicts <color=red>75.00%-1500.00%</color> DMG according to Combo Bonus. Further lowers DEF by {1}% for 10s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts DMG, lowers DEF of single enemy

Skills.Name: Twin Fangs of Fury
Skills.Description: At start of Wave, lowers DEF of all enemies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 60s. Each time DMG is inflicted (CT 5s), lowers DMG Inflicted for all enemies by {1}% for 10s. Further inflicts <code=400,param=200><color=#3398f1>Poison</color> ({2}% of skill user's ATK) for 30s.
Skills.ShortDescription: At start of Wave, lowers DEF of all enemies. Each time DMG is inflicted, lowers DMG Inflicted, inflicts Poison on all enemies
